snippet.title: Uncle Henry's Nuclear Waste Dump for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Uncle Henry's Nuclear Waste Dump is a puzzle game.

The goal is simple: Just do NOT match the same symbols together.


What I think:

A fun game......for a while.
